name: Senka Champion - Zhang De
desc:
This card gains 300 ATK for each monster your opponent controls during its controller's turn only. You can only use these effects of "Senka Champion - Zhang De" once per turn.
● If you control 2 or more "Senka" monsters: You can Special Summon this card from your hand.
● If your opponent controls more monsters than you: You can activate this effect; during this turn, this card can attack monsters your opponent controls twice during each Battle Phase.
